599
00:43:29,005 --> 00:43:31,005
What was the strange thing I said?

600
00:43:34,635 --> 00:43:37,335
I don't know. It was a long time ago. So I don't remember it.

601
00:43:41,775 --> 00:43:42,875
Why?

602
00:43:43,705 --> 00:43:45,135
