00:44:59,605 --> 00:45:01,305
They're both women with initial J.

626
00:45:05,405 --> 00:45:09,935
Reporter Son is such a jerk. This is unbelievable.

627
00:45:10,305 --> 00:45:11,605
I'll go out for a while.

628
00:45:12,035 --> 00:45:15,005
Some people gave an interesting speculation that...

629
00:45:15,035 --> 00:45:19,335
Ms. J is not Mr. Han's lover but his secret ghost writer.

630
00:45:25,175 --> 00:45:27,475
The picture isn't so great.

631
00:45:28,035 --> 00:45:31,405
