632
00:45:31,405 --> 00:45:35,575
We can make her look like his lover, but not his ghost writer.

633
00:45:41,005 --> 00:45:43,405
It's just the first step. You're being too impatient.

634
00:45:43,405 --> 00:45:45,175
Here's your seolleongtang.

635
00:45:45,475 --> 00:45:47,005
It's hot. Be careful.

636
00:45:47,005 --> 00:45:49,675
Can't we get a picture of them together in the writing room?

637
00:45:50,105 --> 00:45:52,875
That means I have to install a candid camera inside his room.

638
00:46:02,005 --> 00:46:04,505
That house has a very high security level.

639
00:46:04,575 --> 00:46:07,275
Why don't we make her work for us?

640
00:46:08,205 --> 00:46:10,205
You need a follow-up article, don't you think?

641
00:46:10,575 --> 00:46:12,805
You need to hear her opinion.

642
00:46:14,375 --> 00:46:18,035
And she'll reveal everything through that article.

643
00:46:18,035 --> 00:46:22,905
If it's too difficult, you can get her as our secret agent.

644
00:46:24,805 --> 00:46:26,335
I'll give it a try.

645
00:46:26,805 --> 00:46:29,135
Nobody hates money.

646
00:46:29,205 --> 00:46:31,775
I'll pay you a generous amount for your work.

647
00:46:49,205 --> 00:46:51,235
I've been through this so many times.

648
00:46:52,305 --> 00:46:55,375
Scandals, plagiarism disputes and ghost writer speculations.

649
00:46:55,535 --> 00:46:58,805
Those rumors have been following me since the debut.

650
00:46:58,805 --> 00:47:01,675
I should be okay, and I don't have to be fooled.

651
00:47:02,505 --> 00:47:06,305
That's it. That's Han Se Ju.

652
00:47:06,305 --> 00:47:08,635
You know that this is the time to fight back with your writing, right?

653
00:47:08,635 --> 00:47:12,675
If you stop publishing the series or your writing becomes boring,

654
00:47:12,675 --> 00:47:15,635
people will think that you get affected...

655
00:47:15,635 --> 00:47:17,875
and that the article is true.

656
00:47:18,005 --> 00:47:20,735
So many people will enjoy gossiping about this.

657
00:47:20,935 --> 00:47:23,305
I won't go easy on that jerk reporter this time.

658
00:47:23,305 --> 00:47:26,035
So don't worry about a thing and just focus on your writing.

659
00:47:26,205 --> 00:47:28,635
You want me to submit the script on time and write what makes money.

660
00:47:28,635 --> 00:47:30,005
What's up with all the editorials?

661
00:47:30,005 --> 00:47:32,005
I'm hanging up. I have to write.

662
00:47:34,775 --> 00:47:36,505
Bring in Attorney Min.

663
00:47:38,005 --> 00:47:40,805
Look into that Jeon Seol.

664
00:47:41,405 --> 00:47:42,935
Get me her number and address.

665
00:48:01,605 --> 00:48:03,035
(Su Hyeon looked at Hui Young and said this.)

666
00:48:12,905 --> 00:48:15,305
(Hui Young's heart pounded...)

667
00:48:16,405 --> 00:48:17,405
(while looking at Su Hyeon.)

668
00:48:37,805 --> 00:48:39,535
If I work with that,

669
00:48:40,205 --> 00:48:41,775
will I be able to write too?

670
00:49:45,205 --> 00:49:46,275
Gosh!

671
00:50:40,235 --> 00:50:42,175
Do you enjoy writing?

672
00:50:43,275 --> 00:50:44,305
No.

673
00:50:45,175 --> 00:50:47,475
What kind of writer do you want to become?

674
00:50:51,475 --> 00:50:53,805
What kind of writer do you want to become?

675
00:50:55,775 --> 00:50:57,735
A writer who doesn't get creative blocks.

676
00:51:21,375 --> 00:51:22,905
What do you think you're doing right now?

677
00:51:27,515 --> 00:51:29,385
What do you think you're doing right now?

678
00:51:34,595 --> 00:51:38,295
Am I caught again?

679
00:51:39,395 --> 00:51:41,065
"Am I caught again?"

680
00:51:42,095 --> 00:51:43,365
You rat!

681
00:51:43,595 --> 00:51:45,365
Mr. Han, wait. Mr. Han.

682
00:51:45,635 --> 00:51:47,695
Please. What are you going to do to me?

683
00:51:47,865 --> 00:51:49,735
You look as if you're about to rip my clothes off.

684
00:51:49,735 --> 00:51:51,965
Answer me. I asked you what you're doing here!

685
00:51:52,095 --> 00:51:54,665
It looked like you were unhappy with the manuscript I wrote.

686
00:51:54,665 --> 00:51:57,865
I saw that you ripped it to pieces, so I was trying to rewrite it.

687
00:51:58,365 --> 00:52:00,635
Who told you to do that? I never gave you permission!

688
00:52:00,635 --> 00:52:03,465
I told myself! Well, I mean...

689
00:52:03,795 --> 00:52:07,395
my heart told me to do it because I wanted to help you.

690
00:52:09,665 --> 00:52:10,695
Get back here.

691
00:52:11,865 --> 00:52:13,135
Can we just talk it out?

692
00:52:13,265 --> 00:52:16,435
Get back here and let me grab you by the collar before I get angrier.

693
00:52:17,035 --> 00:52:19,495
Being grabbed like that is insulting. More importantly,

694
00:52:19,535 --> 00:52:23,465
I won't be able to answer you well as it'll impede breathing.

695
00:52:23,765 --> 00:52:25,965
Is that so? All right, then.

696
00:52:26,935 --> 00:52:29,395
Come have a seat. I said, sit down.

697
00:52:36,265 --> 00:52:39,235
The first question. How did you get in here?

698
00:52:39,835 --> 00:52:43,095
I sneaked in when you were getting home last night.

699
00:52:43,535 --> 00:52:44,635
Last night?

700
00:52:44,865 --> 00:52:49,065
Yes. You seemed to be deep in thought. You didn't even notice.

701
00:52:49,765 --> 00:52:51,995
Are you saying you slept here overnight?

702
00:52:52,335 --> 00:52:54,095
Well, that's...

703
00:52:55,865 --> 00:52:57,595
I have nowhere to go.

704
00:53:04,135 --> 00:53:07,135
I want to kill you now, but I'll do my best to suppress the urge.

705
00:53:08,335 --> 00:53:10,035
Then how did you get in the first day?

706
00:53:11,195 --> 00:53:12,795
Well, that's...

707
00:53:14,365 --> 00:53:16,835
To tell you the truth, I used to be involved in the dark world.

708
00:53:16,835 --> 00:53:19,265
Picking a door lock is a piece of cake for me...

709
00:53:19,265 --> 00:53:22,665
I can kill you this second, but I'll suppress the urge once again.

710
00:53:24,065 --> 00:53:25,395
Who sent you?

711
00:53:26,165 --> 00:53:27,335
Mr. Gal Ji Seok...

712
00:53:27,335 --> 00:53:30,135
I already know that is not true. Who sent you?

713
00:53:34,265 --> 00:53:37,265
It's my doing. I sent myself...

714
00:53:37,935 --> 00:53:39,435
to you.

715
00:53:40,195 --> 00:53:42,035
Is that right?

716
00:53:49,395 --> 00:53:51,365
Gosh, please calm down! If you hit me with it,

717
00:53:51,565 --> 00:53:54,235
I won't be able to answer your question because I'll pass out.

718
00:54:00,295 --> 00:54:02,095
- What do you want? - Pardon me?

719
00:54:02,095 --> 00:54:05,665
I'm sure you're doing this to me for a reason and a goal!

720
00:54:06,495 --> 00:54:08,765
A goal...

721
00:54:10,035 --> 00:54:11,335
Do I have to have one?

722
00:54:11,635 --> 00:54:14,865
- You little... - Gosh! I'll come up with something.

723
00:54:14,865 --> 00:54:16,495
My goal is...

724
00:54:20,765 --> 00:54:24,835
I want to be your friend. Also, I'd like to live here with you.

725
00:54:28,495 --> 00:54:29,735
Get out.

726
00:54:29,795 --> 00:54:33,265
Like I told you a few minutes ago, I have nowhere to go.

727
00:54:34,495 --> 00:54:35,795
You're not going to leave?

728
00:54:36,865 --> 00:54:38,095
I'll call the police, then.

729
00:54:38,635 --> 00:54:40,595
That will cause trouble.

730
00:54:40,595 --> 00:54:43,195
Bingo. I'm calling the police to get you into trouble.

731
00:54:44,095 --> 00:54:46,465
Wouldn't you be in trouble too?

732
00:54:49,335 --> 00:54:51,135
- What? - If the police come,

733
00:54:51,235 --> 00:54:53,865
they'll ask what I was doing here. Then I'll have no choice...

734
00:54:53,865 --> 00:54:57,465
but to tell them that I was writing your manuscript in your place.

735
00:54:58,465 --> 00:55:01,565
Are you threatening me right now?

736
00:55:02,095 --> 00:55:04,865
Did it sound like a threat? I was just stating the fact...

737
00:55:04,865 --> 00:55:05,865
Get out.

738
00:55:08,335 --> 00:55:11,595
I don't need any of this. Take all of it and get out.

739
00:55:11,635 --> 00:55:12,735
Get lost, you punk.

740
00:55:12,735 --> 00:55:15,095
Get out of my sight immediately, you rat!

741
00:55:20,095 --> 00:55:22,665
Shouldn't you decide quickly whether to open the door or not?

742
00:55:22,735 --> 00:55:24,465
If it's Mr. Gal or Ms. Kang,

743
00:55:24,465 --> 00:55:27,135
- they might let themselves in. - Shut your mouth.

744
00:55:31,565 --> 00:55:35,235
Stay right here. If you do anything reckless, you'll die in my hands.

745
00:55:52,035 --> 00:55:54,095
What brings you here?

746
00:55:54,795 --> 00:55:56,395
I want to talk to you about something.

747
00:55:58,495 --> 00:56:00,295
Just a moment, please. I'll be right out.

748
00:56:00,295 --> 00:56:03,935
I don't think you'd want people to hear it. Let's talk inside.

749
00:56:04,495 --> 00:56:06,165
No, we'll talk outside...

750
00:56:06,995 --> 00:56:10,165
It looks like some reporters are on stakeout here. Will you be okay?

751
00:56:17,535 --> 00:56:19,865
Until when are you going to make me wait here?

752
00:56:35,635 --> 00:56:37,295
How have you been?

753
00:56:38,865 --> 00:56:39,935
Good.

754
00:56:40,365 --> 00:56:41,565
What is it about?

755
00:56:43,295 --> 00:56:46,265
Are you going to make me stand here and talk?

756
00:56:48,595 --> 00:56:49,735
Come in.

757
00:57:02,335 --> 00:57:06,195
It's a huge mansion. Do you live here alone without a steward?

758
00:57:08,765 --> 00:57:12,635
I'm extra sensitive these days, so I gave my staff some time off.

759
00:57:14,135 --> 00:57:15,435
Are you stressed out?

760
00:57:16,835 --> 00:57:19,235
I heard you're working on a pretty big project.

761
00:57:19,865 --> 00:57:21,235
What do you want to talk to me about?

762
00:57:22,865 --> 00:57:26,395
It sounds like you want me gone quickly.

763
00:57:26,635 --> 00:57:30,135
You probably had to sneak out to come here because of your wife.

764
00:57:32,465 --> 00:57:35,295
I guess you still deeply resent her.

765
00:57:36,365 --> 00:57:38,595
It sounds like there's some misunderstanding.

766
00:57:40,195 --> 00:57:42,865
I do not resent Ms. Hong.

767
00:57:43,735 --> 00:57:46,765
I can understand her if I work at it.

768
00:57:49,265 --> 00:57:52,535
What woman would want to raise a child...

769
00:57:52,535 --> 00:57:54,595
