770
00:57:55,235 --> 00:57:59,395
A child to whom her husband's first love gave birth.

771
00:58:01,465 --> 00:58:03,335
She was full of suspicion and hated me,

772
00:58:04,295 --> 00:58:06,135
but I think she had more than enough reason.

773
00:58:07,865 --> 00:58:09,035
Right.

774
00:58:10,565 --> 00:58:13,865
Thanks for being understanding.

775
00:58:15,335 --> 00:58:17,295
The person I resent...

776
00:58:20,435 --> 00:58:21,765
is you.

